project_descr: Initial Implementation of Accelerated HCFC Phase Out in the CEIT Region

outputs.output_descr: The aim of the project is to initiate the development of the regional full-sized project document for Ukraine, Belarus, Uzbekistan and Tajikistan to initiate the phase-out of HCFCs and assist countries to stay in compliance with their obligations under the Montreal Protocol.
